<STRONG><U>View Your Employee Information</U></STRONG><BR />
To see current Employee Information on file (e.g. Contact Information, Emergency Contact, etc.) Search your name in the top left search bar. Click on your name with two emoticons beside it to see your employee profile (this is different form your user profile). You can also click on the <i>Employees</i> tab at the top of the screen. Click Go near the top of the screen. Click on your name to see your details. To edit your employee information, Select Edit or talk with the MindField Group HR Team.<BR /><BR />

