<STRONG><U>Submitting Vacation/Sick/Personal Day Requests</U></STRONG><BR />
To submit a Vacation/Sick/Personal Day, you need to do the following:
<UL>
<LI>Navigate to your employee profile</li>
<LI>Scroll to the bottom to the section called PTO/Vacation Requests</li>
<LI>Click the New PTO Request button</li>
<LI>Enter the fields shown on screen, including the number of days off work</li>
<LI>Note that hourly employees are not eligible for paid time off and as such should always select “unpaid”</li>
<LI>Click “Save” and the request will automatically be submitted to your manager for approval.</li> 
<LI>You will be notified, automatically by email, once your request has been approved/rejected</li>
</UL>


