<STRONG><U>View Vacation/Sick/Personal Days You Have</U></STRONG><BR />
Click on the Employees tab at the top of the screen. Click <I>Go</I> near the top of the screen. Click on your name to see your details. Scroll down to the sections named Vacation Days/Personal Days/Sick Days to find your current details. Please talk with the MindField Group HR Team if you have any questions.<BR /><BR />

Vacation days are accrued throughout the year. Sick and Personal days are populated on your start date and are prorated for partial years of service.<BR /><BR />

For employees filing timesheets time taken is calculated from approved timesheets.<BR /><BR />

For employees not filing timesheets time taken is calculated from approved PTO requests, even if the days have not been taken yet.<BR /><BR />




